{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b65a2baea5","title":"第一号号令","origin":"根据文件原件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"85ced78315","index":0,"year":1969,"month":10,"day":18,"articleId":"b65a2baea5"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"adb75e87c3","type":"title","text":"第一号号令","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b65a2baea5"},{"id":"0e0438dd47","type":"appellation","text":"1969年10月18日21时半林副主席指示﹕","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b65a2baea5"},{"id":"b3c7e5a87c","type":"paragraph","text":"一﹑近两天来﹐美帝苏修等有许多异常情况﹐苏修所谓谈判代表团预定明（１９） 日来京﹐我们必须百倍警惕﹐防止苏修搞欺骗﹐尤其19﹑20日应特别注意。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b65a2baea5"},{"id":"4b6cc52224","type":"paragraph","text":"二﹑各军区特别是「三北」各军区对重武器﹐如坦克﹑飞机﹑大炮要立即疏散隐蔽 。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b65a2baea5"},{"id":"3b88c6295f","type":"paragraph","text":"三﹑沿海各军区也应加强戒备﹐防止美帝﹑苏修可能突然袭击﹐不要麻痹大意。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b65a2baea5"},{"id":"2074f3ced3","type":"paragraph","text":"四﹑迅速抓紧布置反坦克兵器的生产﹐如四O(毫米)火箭筒﹑反坦克炮等（包括无后座力 炮和八五[毫米]反坦克炮）。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b65a2baea5"},{"id":"3856bd21a2","type":"paragraph","text":"五﹑立即组织精干的指挥班子﹐进入战时指挥位置。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b65a2baea5"},{"id":"1e993c4781","type":"paragraph","text":"六﹑各级要加强首长值班﹐及时掌握情况。 执行情况﹐迅速报告。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b65a2baea5"}],"page":{"id":"7532de0f5e","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b65a2baea5","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}